  "shortDescription": "Replaces a letter from a String with another letter.",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": [
    "Replaces a letter from a String with another letter.",
    "Example you have the string \"Number 1\" you can chnage it into \"Number 2\".",
    "This is more helpfull in string such as \"Number 7 is a nice number to use.\" it can be change into \"Number 6 is a nice number to use.\".",
    "It also work with letter like in this example \"My favorite letter is F because it looks nice.\" this can be turned into \"My favorite letter is G because it looks nice.\"."
  ],
